304,richardcjarman,2021-09-30,"Excellent airport hotel. The Hampton is a very short walk from the main terminal and is step free, it should take no longer than a couple of minutes. You can reach the city centre and Temple Meads Station by the A1 airport bus which runs very frequently and on which senior citizen passes are accepted.

