328,Deb86,2021-04-30,"Perfect for an early flight Great airport hotel close to the terminal just a 5 minute walk , not much of a menu if you are planning to eat here I would recommend stopping of en route to the airport for food. Maybe a tad pricey for what it is but for ease for a very early flight you can‚Äôt go wrong."
329,whitchurchsue,2020-12-31,"Perfect for Bristol Airport This hotel is 5 minutes walk from Bristol Airport and is ideal for early flights. The staff are amazing, nothing is too much trouble even in these difficult times and they made us feel very welcome. The hotel is clean and well run. Thank you to all the staff for a wonderful couple of days."
330,janetrR8207VV,2020-10-31,"Quick stopover Overnight stay to catch an early flight.  very welcoming, room excellent, quick food service. Would stay again as it‚Äôs so handy for the terminal.  Only downer was getting breakfast, when the dining arrangements weren‚Äôt clear but this was due to COVID."
331,L7768EQdavidd,2020-11-30,"All very good except a bit cold Tuesday 3rd November and we booked to spent the night here due to its proximity to Bristol Airport, we had a 6.00 am check in the following morning. 

We checked in, got our key and made our way to our room. It was reassuring to see a paper seal on the door, which stated that the room had been deeply cleaned, we had to break the seal to enter. 

