342,L9254XAkarenm,2020-09-30,"Perfect 1 night stay before our flight. Very good COVID measures. Hand sanitiser everywhere. Rooms sealed until you enter. Very clean. Food available and quick service. Can‚Äôt fault really. Comfy beds, helpful staff and good sound proofing"
