355,BobsCardiff,2020-03-31,"Heartless Hilton My wife and I used this hotel last December, the night before a flight to Porto and it was excellent, as per my TA post back then. As aresult of that experience, we booked again for March, 2020, prior to our trip to Rome. Covid-19 resulted in easyJet cancelling our flights. We contacted the various providers for our trip and had the following responses:-
