289,chelseapeter25,2022-04-30,"Our Favourite Hotel My partner and I chose this hotel for our April 'just because' stay and it was brilliant. We got a discount for signing up to the Hilton Honours programme directly on their website, making it ¬£253 for 3 nights, which we were happy to pay. Not only was the good price one of our main reasons for choosing it, but also because the location was fantastic. We downloaded the app and were given the opportunity to check in the day before, as well as having easy access to lists of facilities and recommendations etc. 

