343,mfranks911,2021-07-31,"Comfortable Stay, clean and bright rooms and friendly staff A typical non-descript modern building from the outside the Hilton Garden Inn is very convenient for Temple Meads station (just a five minute stroll) and a little further from the harbour's lively facilities and the Town Centre, all in all around fifteen minutes walk from Central Boulelvard.

